result.name: Disney's Hollywood Hotel

reviews.text:
Such a great experience staying in this hotel! Kids love 'em, even adult will also had great time here. Stay at least 2 nights and start feeling the magic moment. The staffs are really nice and helpful,  great facilities for families. The beds are big and the room are clean!
My kids are having great time here, thank you Disney Hollywood Hotel!

Nice clean hotel. Very conveniently located for the parks. Around a mile away so we walked everyday instead of getting the bus. But the bus is very convenient also. The pool is great, as is the whirlpool. My only complain is that there was nowhere to get just a snack. If you wanted a drink you needed to go to the bar. In the US, all the Disney hotels have snack shops inside that sell allsorts of food and drinks. The bar and the restaurants are also very expensive. Otherwise, great staff and atmosphere.

Love this hotel! The rooms are spacious and they even had little bathroom slippers for my daughter. The piano shaped swimming pool is a hoot, as is the lovely pool slide. Chef Mickey came to say hi to is at breakfast too!

Best experience possible. It starts as you walk into the lobby and see the beautiful art deco design and decoration. The staff are very helpful and friendly. Disney artwork all throughout the hotel. A kids area at check in for the kids to watch Disney movies while you check in. Character dining in the restaurant and great rooms.
If going to Disney. Go for minimum 2 days and stay in their hotels they are great

香港にあるディズニーホテルの中でリーズナブルでした。香港ディズニーは開演が遅く開演前から並ぶ必要が無いので、朝食はゆっくりと時間が取れます。このホテルではシェフミッキーのレストランがあり一緒に写真が撮れます。料理も和洋折衷で大満足！
朝早起きして中庭の散歩もお薦めです。

Nice clean hotel. Very conveniently located for the parks. Around a mile away so we walked everyday instead of getting the bus. But the bus is very convenient also. The pool is great, as is the whirlpool. My only complain is that there was nowhere to get just a snack. If you wanted a drink you needed to go to the bar. In the US, all the Disney hotels have snack shops inside that sell allsorts of food and drinks. The bar and the restaurants are also very expensive. Otherwise, great staff and atmosphere.
服務態度親切又很有耐心,不厭其煩的幫忙解決問題,飯店房間裡很乾淨,還有一些愛地球的服務選項(可自行決定床單浴巾是否替換,這點我個人非常喜歡,畢竟自己家都不見得每天換了),房裏插座還備有萬用插頭很貼心,食值得推薦的飯店
酒店不算很新但很乾淨，服務人員親切，床也很舒服，有泳池可以玩水，餐飲價位較貴，接駁車去迪士尼樂園很快又方便

result.name: Hong Kong Disneyland Hotel

reviews.text: Spectacular! worth for money. Nice place; Very clean hotel. All staff were so nice n helpfull. The bed size was pretty big.The pool was so clean n big. My kids very happy stayed here. We really enjoyed the hotel.

Hotel is nicer and newer than I expected from the photos I saw! Rooms are still a little old-fashioned but still comfortable. Great views from the seaview rooms with balcony and the surrounding garden and grounds are very nice as well. Food at the restaurants are very pricey - food at the Walt Cafe is pretty good but the food at the Enchanted Garden is rather sub par. What makes up for it is the Disney characters going around taking pictures with us. Overall a pleasant stay and very convenient for visiting Disneyland.

If you've visited Disney World in Florida, it is a virtual carbon copy of the Magic Kingdom but smaller. Cute but you definitely only need half a day (go later to see the parades). More people were on line to buy things than to go on rides. The Iron Man and Ant Man rides were fun.

Ambiance really nice... But pretty expensive for the ticket. But at least we enjoyed stay there. Food at the banget hall was fine, good for 2 persons in 1 serving... We had a great experienced! Absolutely,  will be back there again soon... Well recommended

Super friendly staff. Club lounge was great value. Fantastic hotel for kids. Swimming pool with slide was great. And kids play area had arts and crafts activities  although only open certain times. Rooms spacious a d lots of attention to detail for kids.

result.name: 香港迪士尼樂園酒店

reviews.text: 公主一定要去的地方💕💕
很好💕💕

6/20入住迪士尼樂園酒店
6/21樂園酒店二位寶貝扮了公主配套了一位港幣1980的專案共二位
6/22快速退房離開了酒店
回國後悲劇發生，由樂園酒店通知二位寶貝拍攝後所選擇的照片沒拿，照片是無法郵寄的需親子或友人於一年內前往樂園酒店領取
8/2委託朋友前往香港迪士尼樂園領取卻告知只有一位寶貝扮公主的照片，請問另一張照片呢？
請香港迪士尼樂園酒店給個回應吧！
